{"testId":14116868,"fileName":"blazemeter_url_test_script.yaml","content":"execution:
  - scenario: default-scenario
    hold-for: 14m
    ramp-up: 1m
    concurrency: 400
    locations:
      us-east4-a: 100
      us-east1-b: 100
      us-west1-a: 100
      us-central1-a: 100
    steps: 4

          Connection: keep-alive
          Sec-Fetch-Dest: document
          Sec-Fetch-Mode: navigate
          Sec-Fetch-Site: none
          Sec-Fetch-User: '?1'
          Upgrade-Insecure-Requests: '1'
